title: Sawbones: Bizarro World
description:
Imagine a world where Sawbones never existed, medical progress was halted and false wellness ran rampant. That's the horrifying world painted by a recent issue of The Times that Dr. Sydnee and Justin are going to guide you through this week.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
